Description: Leaf/grain amaranth cultivar used for greens or seed.
GreenhouseInstructions: Start 2‚Äì4 weeks early for transplants if season is short; harden off before planting.
GrowingAdvice: Direct sow after last frost; thin to 6‚Äì10 in; harvest baby greens 3‚Äì5 weeks.
